 # SAVI Change Log - 2026-05-05
 
+## Release Explore Single-Scope Cleanup
+
+- Created rollback archive:
+  `Docs/Design/ExploreArchive/2026-05-05-before-release-explore-single-scope/`.
+- Removed the `All` / `Mine` Explore scope control from Release/TestFlight
+  builds because Social is hidden and both choices resolve to the user's own
+  saves.
+- Kept `All`, `Mine`, and `Friends` scopes available when
+  `SaviReleaseGate.socialFeaturesEnabled == true` for internal `SAVI Test`
+  social development.
+- Normalized Release Explore scope preferences back to `All` so old `Mine` or
+  `Friends` prefs do not leave beta users in a confusing hidden mode.
+- Updated Release Explore copy to explain the page as a fresh shuffle of links,
+  videos, places, memes, and rabbit holes the user saved.
+- Release iPhoneOS no-sign build passed:
+  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/explore-single-scope-release-iphoneos-nosign-20260505-110909.log`.
+- Captured Release simulator Explore screenshots in light and dark mode:
+  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/explore-single-scope-20260505-111031/explore-light.png`
+  and
+  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/explore-single-scope-20260505-111031/explore-dark.png`.
+
